      "comment": "FORTYHOURS (6) is a filly by Downbytheseaside on debut for leading trainer Andy Gath. Draws widest in the small field but showed ability when runner-up in a trial at this circuit and distance. With even luck she could kick off with a win. BAYSTYLE (5) made a good start to his career five days ago, racing parked but sticking on to be beaten 1.3 metres into second at Maryborough. Open to natural improvement so could go one better. STERLING GIGI (3) is working towards a win having come from this barrier to place behind BAYSTYLE last time out at Maryborough. STOLEN ONE (4) is a filly by Lather Up making her debut for the Mitchell Frost yard. Worth keeping safe.",
